title: [Coast to Coast AM] Ghost to Ghost Collection 1993 - 2013 + Extr
description:
Twenty years of Coast to Coast AM's yearly call in special Ghost to Ghost. Every Halloween, listeners call in with their personal ghost stories to make you laugh out loud or make your blood run cold. This is the complete collection except for this years special which hasn't aired yet obviously.

Also contains Art Bell's Spooky Matter from his short lived Dark Matter Sirius show, as well as the complete Father Malachi Martin Collection, David Paulides 411 Interviews, and the famous Mel's Hole story.



Happy Halloween!
